UAVariable.Description: A string representation of the revision level of a MachineryItem. In most cases, MachineryItems consist of several software components. In that case, information about the software components might be provided as additional information in the address space, including individual revision information. In that case, this property is either not provided or provides an overall software revision level. The value might change during the life-cycle of a MachineryItem.

UAObject.Description: Base class for elements in a stacklight.

UAVariable.Description: Indicates, if the element is contained in the mounting base of the stacklight. All elements contained in the mounting base shall be at the beginning of the list of stack elements.
Enumerate the stacklight elements counting upwards beginning from the base of the stacklight.
Indicates the colour the lamp element has when switched on.
Shows in what way the lamp is used (continuous light, flashing, blinking) when switched on.
Indicates if the signal emitted by the stack element is currently switched on or not.
